OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773508276
OL,3,CPM meets with the Taoiseach in Co Cork
OL,4,Cfor the second UK-Ireland Summit
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister is meeting the
OL,7,FIrish premier in Co Cork for the
OL,8,Fsecond UK-Ireland Summit.
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer was greeted by
OL,11,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin at Fota House
OL,12,Fahead of a series of meetings
OL,13,Finvolving ministers from both
OL,14,Fgovernments.
OL,16,FEarlier, the two leaders visited the
OL,17,FTyndall National Institute, an
OL,18,Felectronics research centre at
OL,19,FUniversity College Cork.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
