PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773508276
OL,3,CPM meets with the Taoiseach in Co Cork
OL,4,Cfor the second UK-Ireland Summit
OL,6,FThe high cost of fuel and energy is
OL,7,Fexpected to dominate discussions which
OL,8,Fwill focus on energy links between
OL,9,FBritain and Ireland.
OL,11,FAn interconnector between Wales and
OL,12,FIreland is expected to provide enough
OL,13,Fpower for 570,000 homes, and represent
OL,14,Fat least #740 million of private
OL,15,Finvestment.
OL,17,FA separate energy connector between
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland and Ireland aims to
OL,19,Flower electricity costs on the island.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773508276
OL,3,CPM meets with the Taoiseach in Co Cork
OL,4,Cfor the second UK-Ireland Summit
OL,6,FThe UK and Irish Governments are also
OL,7,Fexpected to discuss joint exercises to
OL,8,Ftest the resilience of subsea fibre
OL,9,Foptic cables which run between the UK
OL,10,Fand Ireland, and a "crackdown" on
OL,11,Fshadow fleets and other threats in the
OL,12,FIrish and Celtic seas, through a
OL,13,Frefreshed UK-Ireland Defence
OL,14,FMemorandum of Understanding.
OL,16,FOn Thursday, Sir Keir said more than
OL,17,F#900 million of new Irish investment
OL,18,Finto the UK was part of the
OL,19,F"flourishing" ties between Ireland and
OL,20,FBritain.
OL,26,@rD@TOUrD@^O]{D@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
