OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773508276
OL,3,CPM meets with the Taoiseach in Co Cork
OL,4,Cfor the second UK-Ireland Summit
OL,6,FThe #937 million in new investment
OL,7,Ffrom companies in Ireland is expected
OL,8,Fto create about 850 jobs across
OL,9,FLondon, Doncaster, South Wales and
OL,10,FScotland, and covers gas networks, AI
OL,11,Fand cloud-computing, and financial
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FAs the high cost of fuel and energy is
OL,15,Fexpected to dominate discussions at
OL,16,Fthe Cork summit, energy links between
OL,17,FBritain and Ireland will also be
OL,18,Femphasised.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
