FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773508276
OL,3,CPM meets with the Taoiseach in Co Cork
OL,4,Cfor the second UK-Ireland Summit
OL,6,FThe 2026 programme included a business
OL,7,Froundtable event, a civic and cultural
OL,8,Freception, an engagement with the
OL,9,FIreland-UK Youth Forum Advisory Group
OL,10,Fand a research-focused visit.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister is joined by Energy
OL,13,FSecretary Ed Miliband, Environment
OL,14,FSecretary Emma Reynolds, and Business
OL,15,FSecretary Peter Kyle.
OL,17,FSir Keir and Northern Ireland
OL,18,FSecretary Hilary Benn met the region's
OL,19,Fpolitical parties on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
